'From Squeak2.9alpha of 12 June 2000 [latest update: #2449] on 11 July 2000 at 11:05:39 am'!"Change Set:		B3DViewportFix-arDate:			11 July 2000Author:			Andreas RaabA small fix for non-integer viewports."!!B3DVertexRasterizer methodsFor: 'accessing' stamp: 'ar 7/11/2000 11:04'!viewport: aRectangle	| r |	r _ aRectangle.	offset ifNotNil:[r _ r translateBy: offset].	viewport _ B3DViewport origin: r origin truncated corner: r corner truncated.	viewport toggleYScale.! !!B3DHardwareRasterizer methodsFor: 'initialize' stamp: 'ar 7/11/2000 11:05'!viewport: vp	super viewport: vp.	self primSetViewportX: viewport left asInteger			y: viewport top asInteger			w: viewport width asInteger			h: viewport height asInteger.! !